name: Yvette Russell
text:
The Chicken Alfredo Was Pretty Damn Good!!
Good Job And Thank You Kaitlyn!

name: Tiffany Strawn
text: 6.99 for a large one topping pizza!! If you like tasty pizza I'd suggest this place. The kids and I ordered a large one topping and we couldn't hardly finish it. And my boy can eat!!! Great pizza!!

name: Steve Koren
text: Musaletti's is always delicious, hot and a really great value.  It's our favorite local pizza place and our go to for take-out. Staff is always super friendly and helpful as well.

name: Samantha Elliott
text: Great value for the price. They have other offerings besides pizza (e.g., great Greek food). Definitely give it a try!

name: Kevin Tipton
text: Decent Pizza at best.  Slow delivery (I was told 40 mins it took 1.5 Hrs). Delivery driver didn’t understand social distancing, poor attitude.  As for the pizza it was edible that’s why two stars.  Overall a bland pizza.

name: Robert Reffell
text: Tried the carry out special. Fast, hot and delicious. Will definitely come back again.

name: Jeremy Richardson
text: Great pizza for a great price.  We've had it delivered through Door Dash a few times, and my initial expectations were low at $12 for a pie.  However, everyone loved it.  A great delivery option.

name: cathy williams
text: The two people that work there were wearing their masks under their noses. I didn't notice that until after I ordered or I wouldn't have.  I ordered spaghetti and meatballs. It was dry as a bone. The had obviously used the pizza sauce on the spaghetti. The meatballs were good but I wanted pasta with pasta sauce. No flavor... terrible.

name: Emily coulter
text: I have no idea what the problem was here. I wanted to give this small business a chance, and the pizza was great! But the service was awful. The delivery driver got lost and couldnt find my apartment so i cancelled my pizza. The person at …More

name: Vincent Brown
text: Great food. Great prices. Everything cooked to order so call ahead or plan on a short wait.

name: Laura Castaneda
text: No need for extra cheese or peppers on this pizza - they have a delicious blend of spices! A little greasy, but so good!

name: Maria Harewood
text: Great service. They made me 15 pizzas in an hour twice in one day! (Yes, 30 pizzas!) Thank you so much, you made so many people's day! Thank you to the manager working, she was super nice and understanding and staff knew exactly what my …More

name: Paul Boone
text: This pizza is FIRE.  Really really good.  This place and Waldo Pizza have now taken 1st and 2nd for pizza joints in KC for me

name: Ryan Hood
text: Maybe my new go-to. Good pizza, cheaper than all the other local options.

name: tc riley
text: We ordered 2 pizzas and a cheese bread for delivery. The first was a BBQ Hawaiian which has red onions. They were raw strips placed across the top, very gross. The second was an ultimate supreme but it was mostly just sausage. And finally …More

name: David Hawkins
text: I went in for a slice & i was very pleased .. i will be back to try other things on the menu

name: Xavier Fernando
text: Excellent food, but I could see the staff were using their cell phones and feeding themselves FINGERS TO MOUTH in the exact same location right in the heart of the kitchen where they made my food. This is a health code violation, which the entire staff saw, participated in, and permitted. They do not care about your health, sadly.

name: Heather Steele
text: Great pizza, great wings, wonderful staff. The spicy asian wings are my favorite. LOVE THIS PLACE!!!

name: Tommy Vuono
text: Staff were super friendly, it was quick and the prices were amazing! The reason for the 3 stars is that my pizza was cold and kinda dry. May be in part of the margherita not having sauce so that's fair but again it was cold. Gonna order …More

name: Amy L
text: Great food and super fast delivery! Staff is very friendly and my food arrived on time, still hot, and delicious! Wonderful experience especially to be on the weekend where other restaurants have more than  2 hour wait on delivery. Very impressed with the food tried their philly and wings. Definitely going to be ordering more!

name: TheOther RayJ
text: Nice spot for a cheap yet great meal.

name: Nellie Kassebaum
text: Quick and delicious! Better than other chains and same price (or cheaper). Great customer service too.

name: Tyler Woodsome
text: Legitimately the best pizza I've had in KC. Amazing NY style crust, cooked to perfection. These frands know what they're doing. I'm so amped to get more pizzas.

name: JoAnn Horton
text: Worst pizza I've ever eaten, thin crust was soggy. Woke up middle of the night sick tasting rancid pizza.

name: Michael Sanchez
text: This is the best pizza and the best price in the entire city. Glad they are part of the neighborhood now.

name: Hana Kaki
text: Had a Philly cheesesteak, best I’ve ever had! Great menu, lots of options, one-stop shop for fast-food but with dine-in taste! And the staff was great, so that’s a plus-plus!

name: Justin Curtis
text: I live 4 blocks from this place and all 3 times I've ordered delivery the driver can't find it. They are on 39th Street, I am on 39th Terrace. Unbelievable. I'll admit their wings are alright but most recently I got food poisoning from their pizza. Beware.

name: Mia Eats
text: Support local! These guys stand with us in solidarity!

name: Jessica Gentry
text: Was super excited to try the pizza and wings because I had heard good things, the first time we tried to order it was a disaster, but they are new and things happen. The GM Gatta was quick to contact us and make things right. She sent out …More

name: Tyrus Basilone
text: Absolutely the best pizza I've had around here, and for a way better price. About to get some right now

name: Trey Kapfer
text: My new favorite pizza place. Ordered pizza 3 times since they opened about to get some more.

name: Issac Juarez
text: The food was AMAZING here! The customer service was phenomenal and remarkable.

name: Skittle My Pony
text: The 1 topping pizza deal rocks.

text: Amazing pizza and Mozzarella stick's to die for.

text: Very solid pizza at a great price
